_sName: AIM map w/ a bombsite and buyzones.
_sText:
A little AIM map that has a defuse site, and a couple of buyzones.

This is my first map and I made this one with almost zero mapping experience. There's going to be a lot of issues, and I'm open to all sorts of feedback.

If anyone wants to add textures to my map or use the design to create another map, please dm me first!

Let me know if there are any issues, bugs or suggestions!
